ZH: 他的画吊在客厅的墙上。
EN: His painting hangs on the wall in the living room.

ZH: 这幅风景画吊得太高了，我够不着。
EN: The landscape painting hangs too high, I can't reach it.

ZH: 她吊了一条黑色的围巾。
EN: She draped a black scarf.

ZH: 我们吊了彩灯来庆祝节日。
EN: We hung up colorful lights to celebrate the holiday.

ZH: 这块大钟吊在教堂的塔顶上。
EN: The big clock hangs on the tower of the church.

ZH: 他吊在树上的画被风吹倒了。
EN: His painting hanging on the tree was blown down by the wind.

ZH: 她把他的照片吊在自己的房间里。
EN: She hung his photo in her room.

ZH: 老师吊了一幅孩子的作业。
EN: The teacher put up a child's homework.

ZH: 我想吊一块黑板来记录备忘。
EN: I want to hang a blackboard to record memos.

ZH: 他用绳子吊起了一只吊灯。
EN: He used a rope to lift up a chandelier.

ZH: 她原来吊了一副耳环，但后来丢了。
EN: She used to wear a pair of earrings, but then lost them.

ZH: 我发现有人吊走了我的挂历。
EN: I found someone stole my calendar.

ZH: 我们准备在门口吊一幅欢迎的牌子。
EN: We are going to hang a welcoming sign at the door.

ZH: 她吊的衣服总是晒干得很快。
EN: The clothes she hung up always dry quickly in the sun.

ZH: 这家餐厅吊着很多灯笼。
EN: This restaurant has many lanterns hanging up.

ZH: 我喜欢在卧室的墙上吊一些照片。
EN: I like to hang some photos on the wall in the bedroom.

ZH: 每次过年，我们都会吊上红灯笼。
EN: Every Chinese New Year, we would hang up red lanterns.

ZH: 客厅的吊灯照亮整个房间。
EN: The chandelier in the living room lights up the entire room.

ZH: 她的披肩吊在椅子上。
EN: Her shawl is draped over the chair.

ZH: 我们吊了一面大镜子在走廊里。
EN: We hung a big mirror in the hallway.
